PersonalMission.Name: TD-15: Triumph
PersonalMission.Description: When diplomacy fails, the guns start to speak. So get your loaded word in.
PersonalMission.Hint: The more damage you cause in a battle, the better the chance of victory for your team. It is a simple rule that you should remember.

Primary.Conditions: • Cause at least 8,000 HP of damage.
